Jones also exposes the left's weak attempts to blame guns for the violence, in the face of three victims being in fact knifed to death, and in addition to the fact that one person with a gun could have prevented the bloodshed. 

On today's show, Alex also examines former Congressman Alan B. West's intel stating the Benghazi operation was a gun-running scheme, and continues highlighting the latest developments in the Veterans Affairs scandal. -- [I don't think this got covered]
